---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { config } from '../config';
---

<Layout title={`Advisory - ${config.title}`} description="Board director, technology advisor, and startup mentor with 30+ years of experience">
	<section class="advisory-header">
		<h1>Board & Advisory Roles</h1>
		<p class="subtitle">Guiding organizations through technology transformation and growth</p>
	</section>

	<section class="advisory-intro">
		<p>I bring three decades of technology leadership experience to my board and advisory roles, helping organizations navigate digital transformation, AI adoption, and strategic growth. From public company boards to early-stage startups, I provide guidance grounded in real-world experience building and scaling technology companies.</p>
	</section>

	<section class="current-positions">
		<h2>Current Board Positions</h2>
		<div class="positions-grid">
			<article class="position-card featured">
				<div class="company-header">
					<h3>Frost Bank</h3>
					<span class="position-type">Public Company Board</span>
				</div>
				<p class="company-info">NYSE: CFR • Regional Financial Institution</p>
				<p>Serving on the board of this Texas-based financial institution, providing technology and cybersecurity expertise as the banking industry undergoes digital transformation. Frost Bank, with $51 billion in assets, is known for its strong customer relationships and conservative lending practices.</p>
				<div class="position-focus">
					<h4>Focus Areas:</h4>
					<ul>
						<li>Digital banking transformation</li>
						<li>Cybersecurity and risk management</li>
						<li>Technology strategy and innovation</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</article>

			<article class="position-card featured">
				<div class="company-header">
					<h3>James Avery Craftsman Jewelry</h3>
					<span class="position-type">Private Company Board</span>
				</div>
				<p class="company-info">Family-Owned Retail Brand • Since 1954</p>
				<p>Board director for this iconic Texas jewelry brand, helping guide their e-commerce expansion and digital customer experience initiatives. James Avery operates 100+ stores across five states and has built a passionate customer following through quality craftsmanship and meaningful designs.</p>
				<div class="position-focus">
					<h4>Focus Areas:</h4>
					<ul>
						<li>E-commerce and omnichannel strategy</li>
						<li>Digital marketing and customer experience</li>
						<li>Technology infrastructure modernization</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</article>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="advisory-roles">
		<h2>Advisory & Mentorship</h2>
		<div class="advisory-grid">
			<article class="advisory-card">
				<h3>TechStars Mentor</h3>
				<p class="role-duration">Since 2012</p>
				<p>Mentoring early-stage founders through the TechStars accelerator program, focusing on cloud infrastructure, SaaS business models, and scaling technology companies. I've worked with dozens of startups, helping them navigate technical architecture decisions and go-to-market strategies.</p>
			</article>

			<article class="advisory-card">
				<h3>UTSA College of Sciences</h3>
				<p class="role-duration">Founding Member, Advancement Council</p>
				<p>Supporting my alma mater's mission to advance scientific research and education. As a founding member of the advancement council, I help bridge the gap between academic research and industry application, particularly in computer science and AI.</p>
			</article>

			<article class="advisory-card">
				<h3>Early-Stage Investor</h3>
				<p class="role-duration">Cloud & SaaS Focus</p>
				<p>Active angel investor in cloud infrastructure, developer tools, and enterprise SaaS companies. I look for technical founders solving real problems with innovative approaches, and provide both capital and strategic guidance.</p>
			</article>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="expertise-areas">
		<h2>Areas of Expertise</h2>
		<div class="expertise-grid">
			<div class="expertise-card">
				<h3>Technology Strategy</h3>
				<p>From startup to scale-up, I help companies build sustainable technology strategies that align with business objectives.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="expertise-card">
				<h3>Digital Transformation</h3>
				<p>Guiding traditional businesses through the complexities of digital adoption, cloud migration, and AI integration.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="expertise-card">
				<h3>Cybersecurity Governance</h3>
				<p>Ensuring boards understand and properly oversee cybersecurity risks in an increasingly complex threat landscape.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="expertise-card">
				<h3>AI & Innovation</h3>
				<p>Helping organizations understand and harness the potential of AI while managing associated risks and ethical considerations.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="past-experience">
		<h2>Foundation of Experience</h2>
		<p>My advisory work is grounded in decades of operational experience:</p>
		<ul class="experience-list">
			<li><strong>Field CTO at Cloudflare (2021-2025)</strong> - Guided Fortune 500 companies through AI and security transformations</li>
			<li><strong>CTO at Rackspace (2002-2018)</strong> - Built and scaled one of the world's largest cloud companies from startup to IPO</li>
			<li><strong>OpenStack Co-Founder</strong> - Helped create the open-source cloud platform now powering major infrastructure worldwide</li>
			<li><strong>White House Technology Advisor</strong> - Called to assist with critical government technology initiatives</li>
			<li><strong>Congressional Expert Witness</strong> - Testified on cloud computing and technology policy</li>
		</ul>
	</section>

	<section class="advisory-cta">
		<h2>Advisory Opportunities</h2>
		<p>I'm selective about new advisory roles, focusing on organizations where I can make a meaningful impact. I'm particularly interested in companies at the intersection of AI, cloud infrastructure, and cybersecurity.</p>
		<div class="cta-buttons">
			<a href="mailto:jengates@gmail.com?subject=Advisory%20Inquiry" class="cta-btn primary">
				Discuss Advisory Opportunities
			</a>
			<a href="/about" class="cta-btn secondary">
				Full Biography
			</a>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>

<style>
	.advisory-header {
		text-align: center;
		padding: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 6) 0;
		border-bottom: 4px solid var(--color-accent);
		margin-bottom: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 6);
	}

	.subtitle {
		font-size: 1.25rem;
		color: var(--color-text-secondary);
		font-weight: 500;
		letter-spacing: 0.05em;
		margin: 0;
	}

	.advisory-intro {
		max-width: 800px;
		margin: 0 auto calc(var(--grid-unit) * 6) auto;
		text-align: center;
	}

	.advisory-intro p {
		font-size: 1.125rem;
		line-height: 1.8;
	}

	.current-positions {
		margin-bottom: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 8);
	}

	.positions-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(400px, 1fr));
		gap: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 4);
		margin-top: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 4);
	}

	.position-card {
		background-color: var(--color-surface);
		padding: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 4);
		border-radius: calc(var(--grid-unit));
		border: 2px solid var(--color-border);
		transition: all 0.3s ease;
	}

	.position-card.featured {
		border-color: var(--color-accent);
	}

	.position-card:hover {
		transform: translateY(-4px);
		box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
	}

	.company-header {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: space-between;
		align-items: center;
		margin-bottom: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 2);
		flex-wrap: wrap;
		gap: calc(var(--grid-unit));
	}

	.company-header h3 {
		font-size: 1.75rem;
		margin: 0;
		color: var(--color-text-primary);
	}

	.position-type {
		background-color: var(--color-accent);
		color: white;
		padding: calc(var(--grid-unit) / 2) calc(var(--grid-unit));
		font-family: var(--font-heading-secondary);
		font-size: 0.75rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.1em;
		border-radius: 4px;
	}

	.company-info {
		font-family: var(--font-mono);
		font-size: 0.875rem;
		color: var(--color-text-muted);
		margin-bottom: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 2);
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.05em;
	}

	.position-card > p {
		line-height: 1.6;
		margin-bottom: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 3);
	}

	.position-focus h4 {
		font-size: 1rem;
		margin-bottom: calc(var(--grid-unit));
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.05em;
		color: var(--color-text-secondary);
	}

	.position-focus ul {
		list-style: none;
		padding: 0;
		margin: 0;
	}

	.position-focus li {
		padding-left: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 3);
		position: relative;
		margin-bottom: calc(var(--grid-unit) / 2);
		line-height: 1.6;
	}

	.position-focus li::before {
		content: "→";
		position: absolute;
		left: 0;
		color: var(--color-accent);
		font-weight: bold;
	}

	.advisory-roles {
		background-color: var(--color-surface);
		padding: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 6);
		border-radius: calc(var(--grid-unit));
		margin-bottom: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 8);
	}

	.advisory-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
		gap: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 4);
		margin-top: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 4);
	}

	.advisory-card {
		background-color: var(--color-background);
		padding: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 3);
		border-radius: calc(var(--grid-unit));
		border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
	}

	.advisory-card h3 {
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		margin-bottom: calc(var(--grid-unit) / 2);
	}

	.role-duration {
		font-family: var(--font-mono);
		font-size: 0.875rem;
		color: var(--color-text-muted);
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.05em;
		margin-bottom: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 2);
	}

	.advisory-card p:last-child {
		margin: 0;
		line-height: 1.6;
	}

	.expertise-areas {
		margin-bottom: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 8);
	}

	.expertise-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
		gap: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 3);
		margin-top: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 4);
	}

	.expertise-card {
		text-align: center;
		padding: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 3);
		background-color: var(--color-surface);
		border-radius: calc(var(--grid-unit));
		border: 2px solid var(--color-border);
		transition: all 0.3s ease;
	}

	.expertise-card:hover {
		border-color: var(--color-accent);
		transform: translateY(-2px);
	}

	.expertise-card h3 {
		font-size: 1.25rem;
		margin-bottom: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 2);
		color: var(--color-accent);
	}

	.expertise-card p {
		font-size: 1rem;
		line-height: 1.6;
		margin: 0;
	}

	.past-experience {
		background-color: var(--color-surface);
		padding: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 6);
		border-radius: calc(var(--grid-unit));
		margin-bottom: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 8);
	}

	.past-experience > p {
		font-size: 1.125rem;
		margin-bottom: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 3);
	}

	.experience-list {
		list-style: none;
		padding: 0;
		margin: 0;
	}

	.experience-list li {
		padding: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 2) 0;
		border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
		line-height: 1.6;
	}

	.experience-list li:last-child {
		border-bottom: none;
	}

	.experience-list strong {
		color: var(--color-text-primary);
		display: block;
		margin-bottom: calc(var(--grid-unit) / 2);
	}

	.advisory-cta {
		text-align: center;
		margin-bottom: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 8);
	}

	.advisory-cta h2 {
		margin-bottom: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 3);
	}

	.advisory-cta > p {
		font-size: 1.125rem;
		line-height: 1.6;
		max-width: 700px;
		margin: 0 auto calc(var(--grid-unit) * 4) auto;
	}

	.cta-buttons {
		display: flex;
		gap: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 3);
		justify-content: center;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
	}

	.cta-btn {
		font-family: var(--font-heading-secondary);
		font-weight: 700;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.05em;
		padding: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 2) calc(var(--grid-unit) * 4);
		border-radius: 4px;
		transition: all 0.2s ease;
		display: inline-block;
		text-decoration: none;
	}

	.cta-btn.primary {
		background-color: var(--color-accent);
		color: white;
		border: 2px solid var(--color-accent);
	}

	.cta-btn.primary:hover {
		background-color: var(--color-text-primary);
		border-color: var(--color-text-primary);
		transform: translateY(-2px);
		box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
	}

	.cta-btn.secondary {
		background-color: transparent;
		color: var(--color-text-primary);
		border: 2px solid var(--color-border);
	}

	.cta-btn.secondary:hover {
		border-color: var(--color-accent);
		color: var(--color-accent);
		transform: translateY(-2px);
		box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.advisory-header {
			padding: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 4) 0;
		}

		.positions-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}

		.advisory-roles,
		.past-experience {
			padding: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 4) calc(var(--grid-unit) * 2);
		}

		.advisory-grid,
		.expertise-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}
	}

	@media (max-width: 480px) {
		.position-card {
			padding: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 3);
		}

		.company-header {
			flex-direction: column;
			align-items: flex-start;
		}
	}
</style>